                <p class="text-muted fs-5 mb-5">Professional-grade URL management for creators and brands.</p>

                <div class="glass-panel p-4 p-md-5">
                    <form action="/url" method="post" class="row g-3">
                        <div class="col-md-9">
                            <input type="url" name="url" class="form-control smart-input w-100"
