                            <h6 class="fw-bold mb-1 small text-uppercase">1. Request Ingress</h6>
                            <p class="extra-small text-muted mb-0">User clicks your short URL. Our global edge network
                                intercepts the request in &lt;10ms.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="d-flex mb-4">
                        <div class="step-line me-3">
                            <div class="step-dot"></div>
